Package: pergola
Type: Package
Title: Toolbox for Polyploid Genetic Data
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2016-03-31
Authors@R: c(person("Fabian", "Grandke", email = "grafabian@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Dirk", "Metzler", email = "metzler@bio.lmu.de",
  role = "ths"))
Description: Provides tools for linkage mapping in polyploids.
    It implements the method PERGOLA, which is a fast, deterministic method to
    calculate the order of markers in a linkage group.
License: GPL-3
